text: But we - 'Stop your stupid talk, woman!' 'We are -' 'Be silent, woman, and listen, Band Appa Bondi said. 'We know much,' repeated the Chief Captive. 'Some things we will tell you. All who make the journey from the Heavy World become changed. Some die. Most live and grow wings. Between the worlds are many strong rays, not seen or felt, which change our bodies.
